Package: BrewdogR
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper For The Punk API - Brewdog's DIY Beer Recipe Library
Version: 0.1.0
date: 2020-04-15
Authors@R: as.person("Phill Clarke <phill@starkingdom.co.uk> [aut, cre]")
Maintainer: Phill Clarke <phill@starkingdom.co.uk>
Description: A very simple R wrapper around a very simple API.
    The API is called Punk API and is found at https://punkapi.com/. 
    This is a collection of beer brewing recipes from the brewer Brewdog.
    It is regularly published in a less programmatically queriable form as the DIY Dog at https://www.brewdog.com/uk/community/diy-dog.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/phillc73/brewdogr
BugReports: http://www.github.com/phillc73/brewdogr/issues
Imports:
    jsonlite (>= 1.6.1),
    RCurl(>= 1.98-1.1)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
